          <versionCode>00</versionCode>
          <text><![CDATA[<p><b>Worker Ownership, Readiness, and Knowledge Act</b></p> <p>This bill requires the Department of Labor to: (1) establish within the Employment and Training Administration an Employee Ownership and Participation Initiative to promote employee ownership and participation in business decisionmaking; and (2) establish a program that may include grants for outreach, technical assistance, and training, to encourage new and existing state programs to foster employee ownership and participation in business decisionmaking.</p>]]></text>
          <actionDesc>Introduced in House</actionDesc>
        </item>
      </billSummaries>
